text: Serap may refer to: * Serap Aktaş (born 1971), Turkish middle and long- distance runner * Serap Yazıcı (born 1963), Turkish academic * Serap Yücesir (born 1973), Turkish basketball player * Serap (vaccine), a trade name for a diphtheria, pertussis (whooping cough), and tetanus vaccine ==References== Category:Turkish feminine given names
title: Serap
